       FILE             SECTION.
       FD TEST-FILE.
       01 TEST-REC      PIC X(4).
       PROCEDURE        DIVISION.
       DECLARATIVES.
       P01 SECTION.
           USE AFTER ERROR PROCEDURE ON TEST-FILE.
       P02.
           DISPLAY "OK"
           END-DISPLAY.
           GO TO PP02.
